comments: Very well taught and extremely methodical. Could have been more elucidating for psets, but overall was extremely well done.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This is a cool class! You get to learn chemistry things in a different way. The class is mostly grad students, but Udo makes the material very accessible to undergrads as well.
Yes, Udo is a phenomenal teacher. He loves lecturing about the material and goes very in depth on each subject. Honestly, one of the best lecturers in the department.
